Approximate Metric Equivalents for Degrees, Minutes, and Seconds

DEGREE
    1 = 111 km  (or 60 nautical miles)
    0.1 = 11.1 km
    0.01 = 1.11 km (2 decimals, km accuracy)
    0.001 =111 m
    0.0001 = 11.1 m
    0.00001 = 1.11 m
    0.000001 = 0.11 m (7 decimals, cm accuracy)

MINUTE
    1' = 1.85 km  (or 1 nautical mile)
    0.1' = 185 m
    0.01' = 18.5 m
    0.001' = 1.85 m

SECOND
    30" = 900 m
    15" = 450 m
    3" = 90 m
    1" = 30 m
    1/3" = 10 m
    0.1" = 3 m
    1/9" = 3 m
    1/27" = 1 m

